{"tid":259521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"殲10 香港上空攔截美國戰機，迫使美機折返","createTime":"2017-05-27T04:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T05:56:15.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94fd54fe74f62b571a4505d4e5e0cd57548d6b0c","tid":259521,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"美國全國廣播公司（NBC）5月26日報道稱，據美軍官員透露，5月25日在位於香港上空數百英里處，2架中國殲-10戰鬥機對1架美國海軍飛機實施攔截，雙方最近時距離不到100英尺（約合30.5米）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/120422_f4821ff87da93bc95ebb7ccb044f8646.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F120422_f4821ff87da93bc95ebb7ccb044f8646.jpg&h=ae5f96b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國全國廣播公司（NBC）關於此事的報道頁面截圖。<br />\n<br />\n外媒稱，一架中國殲-10戰鬥機在美軍P-3「獵戶座」巡邏機前方約180米處抵近飛行，並做出快速且不規則的連續轉彎動作，從而限制了美軍機的機動能力。美軍官員表示，這一高速攔截行為「非常危險」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/27/120435_78072ceb012a00487fc43b3b2d766129.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F27%2F120435_78072ceb012a00487fc43b3b2d766129.jpg&h=84b57ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fac7a91ebe5b82dd644ba26ea4fc89f0dffc252","tid":259521,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:32:18.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"283d35e4c6d77d605bab9a3cfe2498b292015f04","tid":259521,"uid":23469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"人地美軍黎香港關你中國咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede5b717b50c8f8cdcc2b7aa1ed6b711a9d5b992","tid":259521,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:43:24.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"3e21b89b66ae2f02ec728cd20dbcdce671e032a4","tid":259521,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"